        <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">two</NUMEX> primers rapidly amplifies the signal by <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">as much as 10</NUMEX>
        <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">12</NUMEX>-fold, allowing for direct <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">SNP</ENAMEX> genotyping from small
        quantities of <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">DNA</ENAMEX> target [ <ENAMEX TYPE="LAW">6 11 12</ENAMEX> ] .
        We describe here a simple, scalable assay for SNP
        <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">genotyping</ENAMEX> directly from human <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">genomic DNA</ENAMEX> that uses a
        <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">96</NUMEX>-well plate format and fluorescent primers called
