        been characterized, each for <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">DNA samples</ENAMEX> from <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">192</NUMEX> different
        <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">individuals</ENAMEX>, using this <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">reporter</ENAMEX> assay system. We also
        report that the ERCA allows <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">genotyping</ENAMEX> with <NUMEX TYPE="QUANTITY">as few as âˆ</NUMEX>¼ <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">300</NUMEX>
